public class PlayArea.CardPlacement extends Object implements Comparable<PlayArea.CardPlacement>
Represent a placement of a card. It associates card, chosen side and play area of player.

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(PlayArea.CardPlacement other)
      Compare two PlayArea.CardPlacements based on the placement order.

      If two card placements are adjacent, this can be used to determine which on is on top (it is the one that was placed later).

      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<PlayArea.CardPlacement>
      Parameters:
      other - The other CardPlacement
      Returns:
      A negative number if this was placed before other, a positive number if this was placed after other Should never return 0.
